data.description:
BRING OFFERS! VA Assumable loan @ 3.75%! $5K CLOSING COST INCENTIVE! This luxurious 4 bedroom PLUS loft & office, is perfectly nestled on a cul de sac road, near resort style amenities & the St. Johns River. Upon entering, you are welcomed w/gorgeous wood floors and a large flex room w/french door. Chef's kitchen w/gas stove, granite countertops, food prep island and stainless steel appliances. Sun soaked living area w/custom linear fireplace and casual dining space. Upstairs is a spacious loft w/board and batten accent. Large primary bedroom w/spa like bathroom. Three other bedrooms and thoughtfully remodeled hall bath. Relax in your fully fenced in backyard complete w/extended screened patio wired for TV, pavered deck w/firepit, plus room for a pool! 2 1/2 car tandem garage.
RiverTown is a master planned community nestled along the picturesque Saint Johns River, offering unbelievable resort style amenities - RiverClub provides a riverfront setting with boardwalks, Kayak launch, large pool, onsite café and game room; RiverHouse provides a beautiful clubhouse that is perfect for parties and events, large waterslide pool, lap pool, fitness center, yoga studio and tennis courts; RiverLodge opening summer 2024 with lazy river, gym and much more! Plus, enjoy the dog parks, nature trails, golf cart paths and more.
